ns la préparation au TCF Canada Tests en conditions réelles.</p><div class="flex flex-col gap-4 max-w-md"><a class="flex items-center justify-between bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-blue-600 font-semibold py-4 px-6 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl group" href="/epreuve/expression-ecrite"><span>Sujets Récents D&#x27;expression Écrite</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a><a class="flex items-center justify-between bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-blue-600 font-semibold py-4 px-6 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl group" href="/epreuve/expression-orale"><span>Sujets Récents D&#x27;expression Orale</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class="hidden lg:flex flex-1 justify-end items-end h-full"><div class="relative h-[90%] w-[400px] xl:w-[450px]"><img alt="Ayoub - Expert TCF Canada" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="object-contain object-bottom" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="100vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fayoub-portrait.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fayoub-portrait.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fayoub-portrait.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fayoub-portrait.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fayoub-portrait.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fayoub-portrait.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fayoub-portrait.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fayoub-portrait.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fayoub-portrait.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-8 sm:py-10 bg-gray-50"><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4"><div class="text-center mb-6"><h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Les 4 Épreuves du TCF Canada</h2><p class="text-sm text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Maîtrisez chaque épreuve avec nos entraînements spécialisés et nos simulations en conditions réelles.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3"><a class="group" href="/epreuve/comprehension-orale"><div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 h-full"><div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 p-5"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-headphones w-5 h-5 text-white"><path d="M3 14h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3"></path></svg></div><span class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Compréhension Orale</span></div></div><div class="p-5"><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-4">Écoutez des documents audio et répondez aux questions.</p><div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500 mb-4"><span class="bg-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">39 questions</span><span class="bg-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">35 minutes</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 group-hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"><span>Commencer</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></div></div></div></a><a class="group" href="/epreuve/comprehension-ecrite"><div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 h-full"><div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 p-5"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-book-open w-5 h-5 text-white"><path d="M12 7v14"></path><path d="M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"></path></svg></div><span class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Compréhension Écrite</span></div></div><div class="p-5"><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-4">Lisez des textes et répondez aux questions.</p><div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500 mb-4"><span class="bg-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">39 questions</span><span class="bg-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">60 minutes</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 group-hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"><span>Commencer</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></div></div></div></a><a class="group" href="/epreuve/expression-orale"><div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 h-full"><div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 p-5"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-mic w-5 h-5 text-white"><path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3Z"></path><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"></path><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="19" y2="22"></line></svg></div><span class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Expression Orale</span></div></div><div class="p-5"><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-4">Exprimez-vous oralement sur différents sujets.</p><div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500 mb-4"><span class="bg-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">3 tâches</span><span class="bg-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">12 minutes</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 group-hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"><span>Commencer</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></div></div></div></a><a class="group" href="/epreuve/expression-ecrite"><div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 h-full"><div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 p-5"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-pen-tool w-5 h-5 text-white"><path d="M15.707 21.293a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-1.586-1.586a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.414l5.586-5.586a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 0l1.586 1.586a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.414z"></path><path d="m18 13-1.375-6.874a1 1 0 0 0-.746-.776L3.235 2.028a1 1 0 0 0-1.207 1.207L5.35 15.879a1 1 0 0 0 .776.746L13 18"></path><path d="m2.3 2.3 7.286 7.286"></path><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="2"></circle></svg></div><span class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Expression Écrite</span></div></div><div class="p-5"><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-4">Rédigez des textes de différents types.</p><div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500 mb-4"><span class="bg-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">3 tâches</span><span class="bg-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">60 minutes</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 group-hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"><span>Commencer</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></div></div></div></a></div></div></section><section class="py-8 sm:py-10 bg-white"><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4"><div class="text-center mb-6"><h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Nos Avantages</h2><p class="text-sm text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Tout ce dont vous avez besoin pour réussir votre TCF Canada</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3"><div class="flex gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"><div class="flex-shrink-0"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-trending-up w-5 h-5 text-white"><polyline points="22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17"></polyline><polyline points="16 7 22 7 22 13"></polyline></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Suivi de Progression</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-xs">Suivez vos performances en temps réel et identifiez vos points à améliorer.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"><div class="flex-shrink-0"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-cpu w-5 h-5 text-white"><rect width="16" height="16" x="4" y="4" rx="2"></rect><rect width="6" height="6" x="9" y="9" rx="1"></rect><path d="M15 2v2"></path><path d="M15 20v2"></path><path d="M2 15h2"></path><path d="M2 9h2"></path><path d="M20 15h2"></path><path d="M20 9h2"></path><path d="M9 2v2"></path><path d="M9 20v2"></path></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Simulateur IA</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-xs">Notre simulateur d&#x27;expression écrite corrige vos textes avec l&#x27;intelligence artificielle.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"><div class="flex-shrink-0"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-calendar w-5 h-5 text-white"><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Version 2026</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-xs">Contenus conformes aux dernières mises à jour de l&#x27;examen TCF Canada.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"><div class="flex-shrink-0"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users w-5 h-5 text-white"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Accompagnement Personnalisé</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-xs">Des formateurs expérimentés vous guident vers la réussite.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"><div class="flex-shrink-0"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-award w-5 h-5 text-white"><path d="m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526"></path><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"></circle></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Conditions Réelles</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-xs">Entraînez-vous dans les mêmes conditions que l&#x27;examen officiel.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"><div class="flex-shrink-0"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clock w-5 h-5 text-white"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Accès 24/7</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-xs">Révisez à votre rythme, où que vous soyez, quand vous le souhaitez.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-8 sm:py-10 bg-linear-to-b from-blue-50 to-white"><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6"><div class="text-center mb-6"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium mb-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-target w-3.5 h-3.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle></svg>Préparation Structurée</div><h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Votre Programme de Préparation Personnalisé</h2><p class="text-sm text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Renseignez la date de votre examen et recevez un planning détaillé jour par jour, adapté à votre délai de préparation.</p></div><div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4"><div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-5 border border-gray-100"><h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-calendar w-5 h-5 text-blue-600"><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path></svg>Informations de l&#x27;examen</h3><form class="space-y-6"><div class="space-y-2"><label data-slot="label" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm leading-none select-none group-data-[disabled=true]:pointer-events-none group-data-[disabled=true]:opacity-50 peer-disabled:cursor-not-allowed peer-disabled:opacity-50 text-gray-700 font-medium" for="email">Adresse email *</label><input type="email" data-slot="input" class="file:text-foreground placeholder:text-muted-foreground selection:bg-primary selection:text-primary-foreground dark:bg-input/30 w-full min-w-0 border bg-transparent px-3 py-1 text-base shadow-xs transition-[color,box-shadow] outline-none file:inline-flex file:h-7 file:border-0 file:bg-transparent file:text-sm file:font-medium disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-50 md:text-sm focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive h-12 border-gray-200 focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-blue-500 rounded-xl" id="email" placeholder="votre@email.com" required="" value=""/><p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Votre programme sera envoyé à cette adresse</p></div><div class="space-y-2"><label data-slot="label" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm leading-none select-none group-data-[disabled=true]:pointer-events-none group-data-[disabled=true]:opacity-50 peer-disabled:cursor-not-allowed peer-disabled:opacity-50 text-gray-700 font-medium" for="dateExamen">Date de l&#x27;examen *</label><div class="relative"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-calendar-days absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-gray-400"><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path><path d="M8 14h.01"></path><path d="M12 14h.01"></path><path d="M16 14h.01"></path><path d="M8 18h.01"></path><path d="M12 18h.01"></path><path d="M16 18h.01"></path></svg><input type="date" data-slot="input" class="file:text-foreground placeholder:text-muted-foreground selection:bg-primary selection:text-primary-foreground dark:bg-input/30 w-full min-w-0 border bg-transparent px-3 py-1 text-base shadow-xs transition-[color,box-shadow] outline-none file:inline-flex file:h-7 file:border-0 file:bg-transparent file:text-sm file:font-medium disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-50 md:text-sm focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive pl-10 h-12 border-gray-200 focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-blue-500 rounded-xl" id="dateExamen" min="2026-03-13" required="" value=""/></div></div><div class="space-y-2"><label data-slot="label" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm leading-none select-none group-data-[disabled=true]:pointer-events-none group-data-[disabled=true]:opacity-50 peer-disabled:cursor-not-allowed peer-disabled:opacity-50 text-gray-700 font-medium" for="centreExamen">Centre d&#x27;examen *</label><div class="relative"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-map-pin absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 z-10"><path d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg><select id="centreExamen" class="w-full pl-10 h-12 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-blue-500 bg-white appearance-none cursor-pointer" required=""><option value="" selected="">Sélectionnez votre centre</option><option value="Academy Kuper - Montréal">Academy Kuper - Montréal</option><option value="Collège ELC - Montréal">Collège ELC - Montréal</option><option value="Université Concordia - Montréal">Université Concordia - Montréal</option><option value="Collège Stanislas - Montréal">Collège Stanislas - Montréal</option><option value="Alliance Française de Montréal">Alliance Française de Montréal</option><option value="Université Laval - Complexe X">Université Laval - Complexe X</option><option value="UQTR - Trois-Rivières">UQTR - Trois-Rivières</option><option value="UQTR - Campus Drummondville">UQTR - Campus Drummondville</option><option value="Autre centre agréé">Autre centre agréé</option></select><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 pointer-events-none"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div><div class="space-y-2"><label data-slot="label" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm leading-none select-none group-data-[disabled=true]:pointer-events-none group-data-[disabled=true]:opacity-50 peer-disabled:cursor-not-allowed peer-disabled:opacity-50 text-gray-700 font-medium" for="convocation">Convocation (optionnel)</label><div class="relative"><label for="convocation" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 border-2 border-dashed border-gray-200 rounded-xl cursor-pointer hover:border-blue-400 hover:bg-blue-50/50 transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-upload w-8 h-8 text-gray-400"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path><polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"></polyline><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="3" y2="15"></line></svg><div class="flex-1"><p class="font-medium text-gray-700">Télécharger votre convocation</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-500">PDF, JPG ou PNG (max 5 Mo)</p></div></label><input id="convocation" type="file" accept=".pdf,.jpg,.jpeg,.png" class="hidden"/></div></div><button data-slot="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 shrink-0 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive hover:bg-primary/90 px-4 py-2 has-[&gt;svg]:px-3 w-full h-12 bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-cyan-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/30 transition-all" type="submit" disabled=""><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-send w-5 h-5 mr-2"><path d="M14.536 21.686a.5.5 0 0 0 .937-.024l6.5-19a.496.496 0 0 0-.635-.635l-19 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.024.937l7.93 3.18a2 2 0 0 1 1.112 1.11z"></path><path d="m21.854 2.147-10.94 10.939"></path></svg>Recevoir mon programme</button></form></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 border border-gray-100"><div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text w-5 h-5 text-blue-600"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg>Votre Planning Jour par Jour</h3></div><div class="text-center py-12"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-calendar w-16 h-16 text-gray-300 mx-auto mb-4"><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path></svg><p class="text-gray-500">Renseignez la date de votre examen pour voir votre planning personnalisé jour par jour</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-linear-to-br from-blue-900 to-blue-800"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Le Fondateur</h2><p class="text-blue-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Découvrez l&#x27;expert derrière la plateforme TCF Canada</p></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto"><div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12"><div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center"><div class="flex-shrink-0"><div class="relative"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 rounded-full blur-lg opacity-50"></div><img alt="Ayoub" loading="lazy" width="192" height="192" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="relative w-48 h-48 rounded-full object-cover object-top border-4 border-cyan-400/50" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fayoub-portrait.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fayoub-portrait.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fayoub-portrait.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75"/></div></div><div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Ayoub</h3><p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-4">Fondateur de la plateforme</p><p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Expert en préparation TCF Canada avec plus de 5 ans d&#x27;expérience. A accompagné plus de 25 000 candidats vers la réussite.</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6 justify-center md:justify-start"><span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-300 rounded-full text-sm">Expression Écrite</span><span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-300 rounded-full text-sm">Expression Orale</span><span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-300 rounded-full text-sm">Méthodologie</span></div><div class="flex gap-8 justify-center md:justify-start"><div class="text-center"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users w-5 h-5 text-cyan-400"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg><span class="text-2xl font-bold">25000+</span></div><p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Candidats</p></div><div class="text-center"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-award w-5 h-5 text-cyan-400"><path d="m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526"></path><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"></circle></svg><span class="text-2xl font-bold">95%</span></div><p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Réussite</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Nos Offres</h2><p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Choisissez le pack adapté à votre préparation</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto"><div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow"><div class="absolute top-4 -right-8 w-32 text-center py-1 bg-linear-to-r from-amber-600 to-amber-700 text-white text-xs font-bold transform rotate-45 shadow-md z-10">PACK AYOUB</div><div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 py-6 px-4 text-center"><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Bronze</h3></div><div class="p-6 text-center"><div class="mb-6"><span class="text-gray-600 text-lg">$</span><span class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800">14</span><span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-600 align-top">99</span></div><div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6"><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Compréhension Écrite : <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">40</span> tests d&#x27;entraînement (simulation réelle)</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Compréhension Orale : <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">40</span> tests d&#x27;entraînement (simulation réelle)</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Accès au <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">simulateur</span> d&#x27;expression écrite :<!-- --> <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">3</span> essais inclus</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Expression Orale : Sujets d&#x27;Actualité et Corrections</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Expression écrite : Sujets d&#x27;Actualité et Corrections</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Version <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">2026</span>: Contenus conformes aux dernières mises à jour de l&#x27;examen.</p></div><p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Accès : <!-- -->5 Jours</p><a class="inline-block w-full py-3 bg-linear-to-r from-blue-400 to-blue-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:from-blue-500 hover:to-blue-600 transition-all" href="/checkout/bronze">S&#x27;ABONNER</a></div></div><div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow"><div class="absolute top-4 -right-8 w-32 text-center py-1 bg-linear-to-r from-gray-400 to-gray-500 text-white text-xs font-bold transform rotate-45 shadow-md z-10">PACK AYOUB</div><div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 py-6 px-4 text-center"><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Silver</h3></div><div class="p-6 text-center"><div class="mb-6"><span class="text-gray-600 text-lg">$</span><span class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800">29</span><span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-600 align-top">99</span></div><div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6"><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Compréhension Écrite : <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">40</span> tests d&#x27;entraînement (simulation réelle)</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Compréhension Orale : <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">40</span> tests d&#x27;entraînement (simulation réelle)</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Accès au <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">simulateur</span> d&#x27;expression écrite :<!-- --> <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">8</span> essais inclus</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Expression Orale : Sujets d&#x27;Actualité et Corrections</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Expression écrite : Sujets d&#x27;Actualité et Corrections</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Version <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">2026</span>: Contenus conformes aux dernières mises à jour de l&#x27;examen.</p></div><p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Accès : <!-- -->1 Mois</p><a class="inline-block w-full py-3 bg-linear-to-r from-blue-400 to-blue-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:from-blue-500 hover:to-blue-600 transition-all" href="/checkout/silver">S&#x27;ABONNER</a></div></div><div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow"><div class="absolute top-4 -right-8 w-32 text-center py-1 bg-linear-to-r from-yellow-500 to-yellow-600 text-white text-xs font-bold transform rotate-45 shadow-md z-10">PACK AYOUB</div><div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 py-6 px-4 text-center"><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Gold</h3></div><div class="p-6 text-center"><div class="mb-6"><span class="text-gray-600 text-lg">$</span><span class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800">49</span><span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-600 align-top">99</span></div><div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6"><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Compréhension Écrite : <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">40</span> tests d&#x27;entraînement (simulation réelle)</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Compréhension Orale : <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">40</span> tests d&#x27;entraînement (simulation réelle)</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Accès au <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">simulateur</span> d&#x27;expression écrite :<!-- --> <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">15</span> essais inclus</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Expression Orale : Sujets d&#x27;Actualité et Corrections</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Expression écrite : Sujets d&#x27;Actualité et Corrections</p><p class="pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">Version <span class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">2026</span>: Contenus conformes aux dernières mises à jour de l&#x27;examen.</p></div><p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Accès : <!-- -->2 Mois</p><a class="inline-block w-full py-3 bg-linear-to-r from-blue-400 to-blue-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:from-blue-500 hover:to-blue-600 transition-all" href="/checkout/gold">S&#x27;ABONNER</a></div></div></div><div class="text-center mt-10"><a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors" href="/tarification">Voir tous les détails<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class="py-2 bg-linear-to-b from-slate-50 to-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto"><div class="text-center mb-10"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-award w-4 h-4"><path d="m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526"></path><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"></circle></svg>Outil gratuit</div><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Calculer votre Niveau NCLC</h2><p class="text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Téléversez votre attestation ou entrez vos scores TCF Canada pour connaître instantanément votre niveau NCLC</p></div><div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div data-slot="card" class="bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl py-6 border-2 border-slate-200 shadow-lg"><div data-slot="card-content" class="p-6"><div class="border-2 border-dashed rounded-xl p-6 mb-6 text-center transition-all cursor-pointer border-slate-300 hover:border-primary hover:bg-slate-50"><input id="file-upload" type="file" accept="image/*,.pdf" class="hidden"/><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-upload w-10 h-10 text-slate-400 mx-auto mb-3"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path><polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"></polyline><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="3" y2="15"></line></svg><p class="font-medium text-slate-700">Téléverser votre attestation TCF</p><p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Glissez-déposez ou cliquez pour sélectionner (PDF, JPG, PNG)</p></div><div class="relative mb-6"><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center"><div class="w-full border-t border-slate-200"></div></div><div class="relative flex justify-center"><span class="bg-white px-4 text-sm text-slate-500">ou entrez vos scores manuellement</span></div></div><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text w-5 h-5 text-primary"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg>Vos scores TCF Canada</h3><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-2xl w-10">🎧</span><div class="flex-1"><label data-slot="label" class="items-center gap-2 font-medium select-none group-data-[disabled=true]:pointer-events-none group-data-[disabled=true]:opacity-50 peer-disabled:cursor-not-allowed peer-disabled:opacity-50 text-sm text-slate-600 mb-1 block">Compréhension Orale</label><input type="number