</circle><path d="M12 16v-4"></path><path d="M12 8h.01"></path></svg><p class="text-center">Entrez vos scores pour voir vos niveaux NCLC</p></div></div></div></div><div class="mt-10"><details class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden"><summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-50 font-medium text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-info w-5 h-5 text-primary"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 16v-4"></path><path d="M12 8h.01"></path></svg>Voir le tableau d&#x27;équivalence NCLC complet</summary><div class="px-6 pb-6 overflow-x-auto"><table class="w-full text-sm mt-4"><thead><tr class="bg-slate-800 text-white"><th class="px-4 py-3 text-left rounded-tl-lg">NCLC</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Comp. Écrite</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Exp. Écrite</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Comp. Orale</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center rounded-tr-lg">Exp. Orale</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">10+</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">549<!-- -->-<!-- -->699</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">16<!-- -->-<!-- -->20</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">549<!-- -->-<!-- -->699</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">16<!-- -->-<!-- -->20</td></tr><tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">524<!-- -->-<!-- -->548</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">14<!-- -->-<!-- -->15</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">523<!-- -->-<!-- -->548</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">14<!-- -->-<!-- -->15</td></tr><tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold