"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Questions Fréquentes</h2><p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Les réponses aux questions les plus posées</p></div><div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4"><div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden"><button class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-left"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Les tests sont-ils similaires à l&#x27;examen réel ?</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transition-transform rotate-180"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button><div class="px-5 pb-5 text-gray-600">Oui, nos tests sont conçus pour reproduire exactement les conditions de l&#x27;examen TCF Canada officiel : même format, même durée, même niveau de difficulté.</div></div><div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden"><button class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-left"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Combien de temps pour se préparer au TCF Canada ?</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transition-transform"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button></div><div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden"><button class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-left"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Le simulateur d&#x27;expression écrite corrige-t-il vraiment bien ?</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transition-transform"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button></div><div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden"><button class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-left"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Puis-je accéder à la plateforme depuis mon téléphone ?</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transition-transform"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button></div></div><div class="text-center mt-8"><a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-700" href="/tarification#faq"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-circle w-5 h-5"><path d="M7.9 20A9 9 0 1 0 4 16.1L2 22Z"></path></svg>Voir toutes les questions</a></div></div></section><section class="py-8 bg-linear-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center max-w-5xl mx-auto"><div><h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Besoin d&#x27;Aide ?</h2><p class="text-blue-100 mb-5 text-sm">Notre équipe est disponible pour répondre à toutes vos questions sur la préparation au TCF Canada.</p><div class="space-y-3"><a href="mailto:contact@tcfcanada.com" class="flex items-center gap-4 text-blue-100 hover:text-white transition-colors"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/20 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-mail w-5 h-5 text-white"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"></path></svg></div><div><p class="text-sm text-blue-200">Email</p><p class="font-medium text-white">contact@tcfcanada.com</p></div></a><a href="https://wa.me/1234567890" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-4 text-blue-100 hover:text-white transition-colors" rel="noreferrer"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-400/30 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-circle w-5 h-5 text-green-300"><path d="M7.9 20A9 9 0 1 0 4 16.1L2 22Z"></path></svg></div><div><p class="text-sm text-blue-200">WhatsApp</p><p class="font-medium text-white">+1 234 567 890</p></div></a></div></div><div class="bg-blue-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-5 border border-blue-400/20"><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Envoyez-nous un message</h3><form class="space-y-3"><div><input type="text" placeholder="Votre nom" class="w-full px-3 py-2 bg-blue-800/50 border border-blue-400/30 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-blue-300 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-300 text-sm"/></div><div><input type="email" placeholder="Votre email" class="w-full px-3 py-2 bg-blue-800/50 border border-blue-400/30 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-blue-300 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-300 text-sm"/></div><div><textarea rows="3" placeholder="Votre message" class="w-full px-3 py-2 bg-blue-800/50 border border-blue-400/30 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-blue-300 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-300 resize-none text-sm"></textarea></div><button type="submit" class="w-full py-3 bg-linear-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-400 text-blue-900 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-400/30 transition-all">Envoyer</button></form></div></div></div></section></main><!--$?--><template id="B:1"></template><!--/$--><footer class="w-full bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 py-6 md:py-8"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-6"><div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2"><a class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4" href="/"><img alt="TCF Canada LMS" loading="lazy" width="120" height="50" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="h-12 w-auto" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Ftcf-canada-logo.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Ftcf-canada-logo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Ftcf-canada-logo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75"/></a><p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Maîtrisez les techniques essentielles pour réussir l&#x27;examen TCF Canada avec nos modules interactifs et pratiques réelles.</p><div class="space-y-2"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-mail w-4 h-4"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"></path></svg><a href="mailto:ayoub@tcfcanada.com" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400">ayoub@tcfcanada.com</a></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-phone w-4 h-4"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 